@shazbkhanzdaGEO 9) Let's actually have a look at the FBR Tax/GDP ratio for the first 11 months of each FY:

11MFY18: 9.46%
11MFY19: 8.69%
11MFY20: 8.50%
11MFY21: 8.74%

The ratio dipped in FY19 (BOP crisis left by previous govt) and in FY20 (COVID-19 impact) but picked up in FY21.
